org.odftoolkit.simple.text.list

Class DiscDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.odftoolkit.simple.text.list.BulletDecoratorBase
      • org.odftoolkit.simple.text.list.DiscDecorator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ListDecorator

    public class DiscDecorator
extends BulletDecoratorBase
    DiscDecorator is an implementation of the ListDecorator interface, decorates a given List as disc list. User can extend this class and realize their own list and list item style. For example, set a specifies list item with red color.

    A DiscDecorator can be reused in the same Document.

    0.4
